      "file_path": "kubernetes/consul/resources/config/consul-agent-config/cli-health-check.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 8,
      "message": "The chart doesn't care that it is invalid JSON.  Once it is processed by helm and the tiller pod the {{}} is replaced with a real string.  If then it is invalid JSON you have a problem.  Right now the problem is that this is an invalid yaml helm syntax.\nI am guessing you are using an IDE that lint's JSON?  If so you can ignore the warnings about invalid JSON.  I have the same situation and ignoring/disabling the linter is the only way at this point.",
